@startuml resource-relationships
hide circle
hide empty members
skinparam linetype ortho
title The core clinical record backbone

class Patient [[StructureDefinition-uz-core-patient.html{Open the UZ Core Patient profile}]] #E8F0FE
class EpisodeOfCare [[StructureDefinition-uz-core-episodeofcare.html{Open the UZ Core EpisodeOfCare profile}]] #E8F0FE
class Encounter [[StructureDefinition-uz-core-encounter.html{Open the UZ Core Encounter profile}]] #E8F0FE
class Condition [[StructureDefinition-uz-core-condition.html{Open the UZ Core Condition profile}]] #E8F0FE
class Observation [[StructureDefinition-uz-core-observation.html{Open the UZ Core Observation profile}]] #E8F0FE
class Procedure [[StructureDefinition-uz-core-procedure.html{Open the UZ Core Procedure profile}]] #E8F0FE
class MedicationRequest
class Composition
class Specimen [[StructureDefinition-uz-core-specimen.html{Open the UZ Core Specimen profile}]] #E8F0FE
class ServiceRequest

Patient "1" <-- "0..*" EpisodeOfCare : « patient »
EpisodeOfCare "0..1" <-- "0..*" Encounter : « episodeOfCare »

Encounter "1" <-- "0..*" Condition : « encounter »
Encounter "1" <-- "0..*" Observation : « encounter »
Encounter "1" <-- "0..*" Procedure : « encounter »
Encounter "1" <-- "0..*" MedicationRequest : « encounter »
Encounter "1" <-- "0..1" Composition : « encounter »

Observation "0..*" --> "0..1" Specimen : « specimen »
Specimen "0..*" --> "0..1" ServiceRequest : « request »

note as N
  These are the core record resources, not every
  UZ Core profile. Each arrow points from the
  resource that holds the reference to its target;
  the label is the FHIR reference element.
  Blue boxes are profiled and link to their page;
  grey boxes are referenced but not yet profiled.
end note
@enduml
